      "created_at": "2023-10-20T10:39:30.676Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Thanks very much Alex.  That sounds like the best advice I\u2019ve had so far.  I did feel like I was starting to get bogged down in it all and the fun was waning so I think I\u2019ll do what you suggest and go back to what I started off doing.  Just cycling and not worrying about it too much, and keeping in mind my breathing so I don\u2019t push the intensity too far.</p>",
