      "cooked": "<p>Thanks Alex.</p>\n<p>I don\u2019t get any resistance reading on the screen at all so I guess the only way for me to do it is to set it to a set number of turns and do the test that way.<br>\nI am generally using 3 full turns at the moment as what feels comfortable so I can leave it there and see how that goes for the test.</p>",
