      "created_at": "2023-10-20T15:01:41.443Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yeah, unfortunately I thought they were like for like in terms of the power meter, certainly considering they cost the same, so I\u2019m a bit disappointed in that regard, but I just have to work with it now <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"><br>\nHopefully in terms of long term build quality it will make up for it.</p>",
