      "created_at": "2023-10-20T15:16:55.916Z",
      "cooked": "<p><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/rofl.png?v=9\" title=\":rofl:\" class=\"emoji only-emoji\" alt=\":rofl:\"><br>\nMaybe I can look into the options.  I really thought it had a comparable power meter so that\u2019s a bit annoying.</p>\n<p>Are these stick on meters like from Wahoo or Garmin any better or are proper power pedals the only decent option?</p>",
