      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2023-10-20T15:19:18.052Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I think power meter pedals are the only decent option.  I don\u2019t think there is such a thing a stick on power meter. For a regular bike with highend cranks you can get crank arm ones but that does not help you.  Favero Assioma single side seems to be the preferred option but that and shoes and it is still expensive.</p>\n<p>There are cadence and speed sensors but those won\u2019t provide you any more accuracy than you have now.</p>",
      "post_number": 19,
      "post_type": 1,
